data.title: Mohit Malik
data.meta_description: Mohit Malik is an Indian actor who mainly works in Hindi television. He is best known for his role of Samrat Singh Rathore in Doli Armaano Ki, Sikandar Singh Gill in Kullfi Kumarr Bajewala and Kunal Malhotra in Baatein Kuch Ankahee Si.
